        <!-- DEATH SECTION -->
        <div id="death">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12 section-title">DEATH</div>
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <blockquote>
                            "If one day speed kills me, don't cry. Because I was smiling."
                            <footer>- Paul Walker</footer>
                        </blockquote>
                        <p>Paul Walker died in a single-car crash on November 30, 2013, at the age of 40. The car he was riding in, a Porsche Carrera GT, crashed into a concrete lamppost and two trees on Hercules Street, in Santa Clarita, California. Walker and the driver, his friend Roger Rodas, were both pronounced dead at the scene of the accident.</p>
                        <p>Walker's sudden death led to an outpouring of tributes from his fans and fellow celebrities. His contributions to the Fast & Furious franchise were honored, and his legacy continues to be celebrated by fans around the world.</p>
                        <p>For more information, visit the official <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Walker" target="_blank">Wikipedia page</a>.</p>
                    </div>
